est includes neoliberalism, sanctification of personal interests, high welfare and so on.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999999673948429, \"rank\": 2.0005938027814376e-08, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999994028605179, \"rank\": 5.971399173528654e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Satan\", \"score\": 0.9999989154777237, \"rank\": 1.0845230762938258e-06, \"text\": \"Satan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Satan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Satan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a \\\"theatre\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"political correctness\", \"from\": 440, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"neoliberalism\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"sanctification\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"personal interests\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"high welfare\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To focus on high welfare is actually a trap.\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"high welfare\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 585}, {\"ngram\": \"a trap\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the West successfully disintegrated the Soviet Union and ruthlessly looted and plundered a huge amount of Soviet property and resources, it quickly gave itself a variety of high welfare.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 658, 